quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,17,un ki misaal is shakhs ki si hai ke jis ne ( shab_e_ tareek mein ) aag jalayi. jab aag ne is ke ird gird ki cheeze roshan kee to khuda ne un ki roshni zael kar di aur un ko andheron mein chore diya ke kuch nahi dekhte
  2,18,"( yeh ) behray hain, gungay hain, andhay hain ke ( kisi terhan seedhay raste ki taraf ) lout hi nahi satke"
  2,19,ya un ki misaal meen ki si hai ke aasman se ( baras raha ho aur ) is mein andheray par andhera ( chhaa raha ) ho aur ( baadal ) garaj ( raha ) ho aur bijli ( kond rahi ) ho to yeh kadak se ( dar kar ) mout ke khauf se kaanon mein ungelian day len aur allah kafiroon ko ( har taraf se ) ghairay hue hai
  2,20,qareeb hai ke bijli ( ki chamak ) un ki aankhon ( ki Basarat ) ko uchak le jaye. jab bijli ( chamakti aur ) un par roshni daali hai to is mein chal parte hain aur jab andhera ho jata hai to kharray ke kharray reh jatay hain aur agar allah chahta to un ke kaanon ( ki shanwai ) aur aankhon ( ki benaye dono ) ko zael kar deta hai. be shak allah har cheez par Qadir hai
  2,21,logo! apne perwar-digaar ki abat karo jis ne tum ko aur tum se pehlay logon ko pedakiya taakay tum ( is ke azaab se ) bachcho
  2,22,jis ne tumhare liye zameen ko bichona aur aasman ko chhat banaya aur aasman se meen barsa kar tumahray khanay ke liye anwaa o aqsam ke meway peda kiye. pas kisi ko khuda ka humsar nah banaao. aur tum jantay to ho
  2,23,"aur agar tum ko is ( kitaab ) mein, jo hum ne apne bande ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam arabi ) par nazil farmai hai kuch shak ho to isi terhan ki aik sourat tum bhi bana lao aur khuda ke siwa jo tumahray madadgaar hon un ko bhi bulalo agar tum sachey ho"
  2,24,lekin agar ( aisa ) nah kar sakuu aur hargiz nahi kar sakuu ge to is aag se daro jis ka eendhan aadmi aur pathar hon ge ( aur jo ) kafiroon ke liye tayyar ki gayi hai
